<p>For fall 2020, Gola and retailer Anthropologie collaborated on two exclusive styles.</p>

<p> GOLA X ANTHROPOLOGIE DROPS 2 STYLES</p>

<p>For fall 2020, Gola and retailer Anthropologie collaborated on two exclusive styles. </p>

<p>Taking one of Gola’s most popular styles (Orchid II), the team at Anthropologie added colors and details to make the style pop with any look.</p>

<p>This collab elevates the sneaker game by reimagining the basic leather tennis shoe with rainbow, metallic spots and metallic silver zebra print. </p>

<p>They retail for $90. </p>

